# Map upstream Requires-Dist names that Noble's default dh_python3
# fallback table does not carry to their Avalan-PPA Debian packages.
#
# huggingface_hub is the canonical case here: dh_python3 cannot map
# the PyPI name to python3-huggingface-hub without this hint because
# python3-huggingface-hub is not in Noble's archive (it lives only in
# the Avalan PPA), so the system fallback table on the builder has no
# entry for it. Without the override, python3-diffusers' generated
# Depends omits python3-huggingface-hub and an apt-get install of
# avalan ends up missing the module that avalan.model.hubs.huggingface
# imports at runtime.
huggingface-hub python3-huggingface-hub
